frontmatter.title: Layer5 Joins the CNCF
frontmatter.author: The Newsroom
frontmatter.description: Layer5 officially becomes a member of the Cloud Native Computing Foundation (CNCF). Since its inception, Layer5 has actively contributed to and supported CNCF initiatives and projects.
